- [x] **End-to-End Chat CLI Test**: The [chat_cli.py](file:///d:/lattice-brain/scripts/chat_cli.py) executes smoothly with active SQLite storage and the offline router fallback functioning. 

*Lattice Brain is now stable and fully ready.*
